      "title": "Evaluation of investor attractiveness of power-generating companies: special reference to the development risks of the electric power industry",
      "abstract": "The paper presents the author’s methodical approach to the investor attractiveness evaluation of power-generating companies on the basis of risks development decomposition, which can calculate the value of risks in the financing of electricity capital projects."
